Vale in Discussions to Sell Its 19 Mega Ships, CEO Tells O Globo

-- B y   J u a n   P a b l o   S p i n e t t o
-- 
2011-12-09T11:06:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/vale-in-discussions-to-sell-its-19-mega-ships-ceo-tells-o-globo.html
Vale SA  is in “advanced”
negotiations to sell its fleet of 19 mega iron-ore vessels,
Chief Executive Officer Murilo Ferreira said in an interview
with  O Globo .  Vale is holding talks with a non-Brazilian company, the CEO
told the Rio de Janeiro-based newspaper. Vale will only sell the
ships if it can lease them back under long-term contracts, O
Globo said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Juan Pablo Spinetto in Rio de Janeiro at 
 jspinetto@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net  